social_posts.post_text: Never in a million years did I think this many people in this many places would listen to songs I wrote. Thank y’all for listening. It’s been a hell of a year 🤘🏼

2022. What a dang year. It tested my patience. It made me a better husband, a more experienced songwriter, but most importantly it made me a dad. It opened my eyes to a world I never thought I would flourish in. All in all it was a whirlwind and I can’t wait to see what 2023 has in store for this little family. Happy New Year everybody!
Had a dang good time writin this song with the man himself. Album out today! Link is in my bio to stream this thing. Turn it up! #35s

Super thankful for this opportunity to partner up with @ctmentertainment and @younggunspub to kick the futures ass. Couldn’t have asked for a more talented group of people in my corner. Let’s go team!!!
Happy Easter everybody! Hope everyone is getting a good dose of Jesus and family today ✝️

Get Her Back out now!! Crazy how some songs find the perfect home. Shoutout to @kendalllettow for pitching this thing. @michaelraymusic you sang the shit outta this. @musicknox produced this into a serious record. Wrote it with @dallaswilson8 @laloguzmanjr and @iam_jordanjames 🍻

Proud of this dude and these songs! Checkout the new ep out today. Helped write tracks 2, 4, and 5 and it’s crazy to see them come to life like this. Y’all killed it!! @michaelraymusic @musicknox @megpatrickmusic #dontgiveatruck #getherback #spiritsanddemons

So grateful I get to wake up every day and write country songs. Grateful for good friends and co-writers that bring in great ideas and melodies and trust I won’t screw it up. @allisonveltzcruz @alexanderpalmer 

Shoutout to @michaelraymusic @musicknox and @megpatrickmusic for slaying this record. Can’t wait to see where this song goes at radio 🙏🏼

I’ve been a @jasonaldean fan since day one, so it’s always crazy hearing him sing something I wrote! Y’all go check out the #HighwayDesperado album out today and especially track 8 #ImOverYou 

Pumped to have written this with my boys @imjoshphillips and @micahwilshire 

Shoutout to @musicknox for bringing it to a new level like always 

Badass playing by @kurtallison @tullykennedy @richredmond @shoenfeld and everyone else on the session that day 🙏🏼
Thankful for this family that God has blessed me with 🤎

So grateful to be a part of this song, but there’s nothing like watching your friend catch a dream after chasing it for years. You’ve busted your ass and sacrificed a ton, but every minute was worth it. Cheers to the start of something great 🍻
